line 55 is literally your 55th line of your (code~text) file, and the position is your character space (starting from the left).

* I recommend you download notepad++ ( <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://notepad-plus-plus.org/">http://notepad-plus-plus.org/</a><!-- m --> ), as it's really useful. Once you got it up, choose for the (programming) language (bar at the top of the screen): XML

